{"tid":733942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2孩子坐關愛座　廢老屌小孩爸：兒童不能坐","createTime":"2018-07-08T08:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T08:17:49.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f60fb036426f43d18bdce048f31c8d2e561d8634","tid":733942,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:13:07.000Z","msg":"父親帶2個孩子搭捷運，讓他們坐在博愛座，沒想到竟被嗆「不能坐！」<br />\n一名男網友在臉書「爆怨公社」社團上傳照片，就讀大班和小一的孩子坐在捷運博愛座，「幹我竟然被該死的老女人嗆：『兒童不能坐博愛座！』」讓他氣得大罵髒話。原po不滿，「旁邊還一堆位置是在大聲什麼。」<br />\n<br />\n許多網友也罵：「每個位子都可以是博愛座」、「她國文不好，不懂什麼叫孺&hellip;」、「又不是老人座，不用鳥她」、「要我，我會要小孩絕對不要起來」、「老 弱 婦 孺，博愛座的需要，國小就教這四個字 ，是不是不知道的都上課都在混？」<br />\n也有網友說：「真的不喜歡博愛座這個名稱，明明是好意，結果卻一堆老人倚老賣老。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180708/1387380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180708%2F1387380&d=noIlqJJ4x7g3p1CSapflrY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=e604c2f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180708%2F1387380&h=d4588b0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180708/1387380</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 惡過關愛座巴打"},{"pid":"bf89f9dbea18d147c7a4f8541bda9ee28bfc7198","tid":733942,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"孩子誓言長大後要成為關愛座hunter"},{"pid":"3db05420c6494d1e1127efc1f6eb4946c7bc38e4","tid":733942,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bf89f9dbea18d147c7a4f8541bda9ee28bfc7198","tid":733942,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"孩子誓言長大後要成為關愛座hunter"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"原來關蛇有童年陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45326b3421eb174386ed21ae2e8242847d1a20a1","tid":733942,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"